'''綿蟹派'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|Dromiacea}}）是[[十足目|十足目]][[短尾下目|短尾下目]]下的一個節，包含240種現存的和約300已滅絕的[[蟹|蟹]]<ref name="Grave">{{cite journal |journal=[[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |year=2009 |volume=Suppl. 21 |pages=1–109 |title=A classification of living and fossil genera of decapod crustaceans |first1=Sammy |last1=de Grave |first2=N. Dean |last2=Pentcheff |first3=Shane T. |last3=Ahyong |language=en |url=http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |display-authors=etal |access-date=2013-04-12 |archive-date=2011-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606064728/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s21/s21rbz1-109.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。綿蟹派和[[綿蟹亞派|綿蟹亞派]]、[[圓關公蟹派|圓關公蟹派]]被認為來自同一個[[單系群|單系群]]，但是[[形態學|形態學]]研究得出了相反的结论。<ref name="Grave"/>

綿蟹派的[[化石記錄|化石記錄]]最少可以追溯到[[侏羅紀|侏羅紀]]，<ref>{{cite journal |title=On the influence of fishes on the evolution of benthic crustaceans |author=J. W. Wägele |journal=[[Journal_of_Zoological_Systematics_and_Evolutionary_Research|Journal of Zoological Systematics and Evolutionary Research]] |volume=27 |issue=4 |pages=297–309 |doi=10.1111/j.1439-0469.1989.tb00352.x}}</ref>如果''Imocaris''被確實為該節的成員，那麼其歷史便可以追溯到[[石炭紀|石炭紀]]。<ref>{{cite journal |author=[[Frederick_Schram|Frederick Schram]] & Royal Mapes |year=1984 |title=''Imocaris tuberculata'', n. gen., n. sp. (Crustacea: Decapoda) from the upper Mississippian Imo Formation, Arkansas |journal=[[Transactions_of_the_San_Diego_Society_of_Natural_History|Transactions of the San Diego Society of Natural History]] |volume=20 |issue=11 |pages=165–168}}</ref>

現屬[[十足目|十足目]][[歪尾派|歪尾派]]的亞科Eocarcinoidea以及其中的兩個属（''Eocarcinus''和''Platykotta''）最初也是被劃分在綿蟹派下的。<ref name="Chablais">{{cite journal |author=Jérôme Chablais, Rodney M. Feldmann & Carrie E. Schweitzer |year=2011 |title=A new Triassic decapod, ''Platykotta akaina'', from the Arabian shelf of the northern United Arab Emirates: earliest occurrence of the Anomura |journal=[[Paläontologische_Zeitschrift|Paläontologische Zeitschrift]] |volume=85 |pages=93–102 |doi=10.1007/s12542-010-0080-y |url=http://decapoda.nhm.org/pdfs/31744/31744.pdf |format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]] |access-date=2013-04-12 |archive-date=2017-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703125836/https://decapoda.nhm.org/pdfs/31744/31744.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

